metadata.name: METANIME BOOK
metadata.description: Are you ready for the Metanime battle? Each NFT in the collection has 6 attributes, each attribute gives a greater or lesser % winrate in relation to the rarity of it. The rarer your NFT is the more passive income, it will bring you with our automatic Fight 2 earn. Each NFTs will give you the opportunity to play our P2E and fight our of 10 bosses.
